data.description: Charming Bungalow in the Heart of Artesia. The house offers 3 bedrooms, 1.75 bathrooms. Property had upgrades in 2015, kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, ceramic tile, windows, exterior paint, water heater and washer and dryer hookups. Long driveway for plenty of parking enough for a few cars. ****** Motivated Seller, bring your buyers. " The house is rented out at the moment, the tenant are currently paying 2300 plus utilities, lease will end in February. Seller would like for him to stay until then.
